https://arkinidev.github.io/Keyboard-Sounds/
To make it a application please follow these steps:
-------------------------------------------
Chrome/Google Browser:
1. When you are at the website you want to click on the three dots at the top right of your browser.
2. You should now see a dropdown appear, now click on the save and share button, then click on "add shortcut" then you want to name it somthing like "Keyboard Sounds" feel free to name it what you want.
3. Now click the open as window button and then ok. Now press windows to open the popup menu then search for what you named the shortcut, in my case that would be "Keyboard Sounds".
4. And there you Go, now you can play around with it and more updates will of course be coming soon :)
-------------------------------------------
